College Nationals: Women

Posted on Thursday, May 24, 2007

The women are on their second day of the nationals today. Dartmouth started off rocky, but we seem to be recovering lead by some sailing by Adele Wilhelm and Kate Hacker in B division. Follow the results online. Update: The women finished 12th.
